title: Rebuild Nixos
tags: @zettel _method nixos
roam-id: b97fb469-826f-4a72-92c7-4643fff85c5b
type: text/markdown

- if you have your `configuration.nix` under `/etc/nixos` (which normally is the case) then use the following

  ``` bash
  sudo nixos-rebuild switch
  ```

- but if you have your `configuration.nix` file in some other location then you need to specify by doing

  ``` bash
  sudo nixos-rebuild switch -I nixos-config="/path/to/configuration.nix"
  ```
